Package controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddPartsController
    This class the Add Parts Controller, used to orchestrate the the add parts form.
    AddProductsController
    This is the add products controller that orchestrates the add products form.
    Controller
    This is the main controller for the application and orchestrates the main form as well as provides public static variables for modifying parts and products.
    Counter
    This class is used as a global counter to generate and distribute new unique product and part ID's.
    InHouse
    This class is an extension of the part class and inherits several attributes from it.
    Inventory
    This is the Inventory class and it is used to manage all of the data within the tables and Observable lists in this project.
    ModifyPartsController
    This is the modify parts controller used to orchestrate everything on the modify parts form.
    ModifyProductsController
    This is the modify products controller.
    Outsourced
    This class is an extension of the part class and inherits several attributes from it.
